OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA day of bright or sunny spells
OL,6,Fand a scattering of showers across the
OL,7,Fregion. The showers mainly light but a
OL,8,Ffew heavier showers possible. Feeling
OL,9,Fa little warmer than of late.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FShowers fading this evening
OL,12,Facross the south, but a few continuing
OL,13,Fovernight in the north. Clear spells
OL,14,Fdeveloping away from the showers,
OL,15,Fallowing it to turn chilly in the
OL,16,Fcountryside.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
