OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA dry and bright start in
OL,6,Fthe south, but showery rain will
OL,7,Fspread across the region throughout
OL,8,Fthe day. The odd heavier shower
OL,9,Fpossible, but feeling warm in any
OL,10,Fsunshine.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FDrier
OL,13,Fbut cooler on Sunday, with a cold
OL,14,Fnight following. Staying cool early
OL,15,Fnext week, with some further spells of
OL,16,Frain but also some sunshine at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
